---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import siteData from '../../data/site.json';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description={`${siteData.name} affiliate disclosure policy. Learn how we earn from affiliate partnerships and how it affects our recommendations.`}
>
  <Section narrow>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-gray max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Transparency matters to us. Here's how {siteData.name} earns money and how that relates to our recommendations.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Earn</h2>
      <p>
        {siteData.name} participates in various affiliate marketing programs. This means that when you click on certain links on our site and make a purchase, we may receive a small commission from the retailer or service provider.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>This comes at absolutely no extra cost to you.</strong> The price you pay is the same whether you use our affiliate link or go directly to the retailer's website.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Editorial Independence</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate commissions never influence our product ratings, rankings, or recommendations. Our editorial process is completely independent of our monetization:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>We research and evaluate products based on their merits.</li>
        <li>We include products in our recommendations because they're genuinely good — not because they pay higher commissions.</li>
        <li>We always disclose both positives and negatives.</li>
        <li>If a product doesn't meet our standards, it won't be recommended regardless of commission rates.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Affiliate Programs We Participate In</h2>
      <p>
        We may participate in affiliate programs including, but not limited to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Amazon Associates Program</li>
        <li>Other affiliate networks and direct brand partnerships</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>FTC Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission (FTC) guidelines, we disclose that some of the links on {siteData.name} are affiliate links. We are a participant in various affiliate programs designed to provide a means for sites to earn commissions by linking to products and services.
      </p>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships or editorial process, please don't hesitate to <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
